Live Community FOMO
Teknologi: Supabase Realtime + WebSockets

javascript
// Broadcast ke semua user saat ada yang bidding
supabase.channel('nft-123')
  .on('broadcast', { event: 'new_bid' }, (payload) => {
    showPopup(`${payload.user} baru saja bid Rp ${payload.amount}!`);
  })
