Builder.io Editor - PUYOK Hero

âš¡ Version Control untuk Video
Scenario	Video	Overlay
Desktop	1080p MP4	Gradient 135deg
Mobile	Vertical MP4	Solid dark
Low BW	Static image	Full dark
