   - [Starter Kit PUYOK](https://github.com/puyok-starter/mvp)
3. **Task Breakdown**:
   - [x] Setup proyek (1 jam)
   - [ ] Implementasi auth (3 jam)
   - [ ] Halaman marketplace (8 jam)
   - [ ] Integrasi escrow (6 jam)
### ğŸ“Œ Catatan:
